      "content": "yeah i get that. it just feels like everything is breaking down at once. i'm seeing so many announcements and flight boards just changing constantly... it's super stressful. is there any way to predict if a flight will be one of those \"risky\" ones before I actually book it? like is there a specific pattern to why these things go sideways?",
